#Download scikit-learn:
pip install -U scikit-learn  # you might need to use sudo

# you will nedd to insall the following modules:

pip install numpy  # fundamental data structures
pip install scipy  # supports data manipilation and analysis
pip install matplotlib # plotting library
pip instal pandas # reading and writing data in different formats


# you can tell a module is installed in python by:

>> import <modulename>


if there is no complaint then the module is installed succesfully


